// ==UserScript==
// @name         TM Script Manager
// @namespace    https://github.com/THVjQ
// @version      1.6.0
// @description  Loads and manages all custom scripts from GitHub with a right-edge pull-tab UI, API key storage, and a scan button that finds updates + newly published scripts
// @author       THVjQ
// @match        *://*/*
// @grant        GM_setValue
// @grant        GM_getValue
// @grant        GM_xmlhttpRequest
// @grant        GM_addValueChangeListener
// @grant        GM_openInTab
// Child scripts are eval'd inside THIS manager's sandbox, so the per-script
// connect rules in their own headers are stripped — network access is
// governed by the list below. '*' lets any managed script reach its backend
// (e.g. the SMS Bridge server); named hosts document what's used today.
// @connect      raw.githubusercontent.com
// @connect      api.github.com
// @connect      sosmessenger.thvjq.com.au
// @connect      *
// @run-at       document-idle
// ==/UserScript==

